e=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6b9ac7f7\" data-id=\"6b9ac7f7\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14ff91ec elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"14ff91ec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Brooks is a real estate agent in the Austin, Texas market whose main focus is the client journey and differentiating himself in the marketplace. He began his career out of a passion for real estate and helping his clients achieve their personal and financial goals. His core values include faith, family, impacting others, and fitness. Brooks saw an opportunity to provide a one-of-a-kind service and experience to his clients and decided to begin his journey in Real Estate.<\/p><p>At a young age, he was dedicated to the sport of swimming. He went on to compete at the collegiate level at the University of Louisville where he won two conference championships and became team captain in his final year at U of L. His professional career began in the IT staffing and services industry connecting companies and organizations with top talent in IT. Both recruiting and account management have given Brooks a unique start to his career. He later went on to become the Director of Business Development for his family\u2019s Oil and Gas Landman brokerage company in west Texas where he impacted their company footprint, developed client relationships, and increased their clients\u2019 overall production and land management. In 2020, Brooks decided that it was time to pursue his passion and take the next step to start his career in Real Estate. As a real estate practitioner, his focus is rooted in developing relationships with his clients, providing a unique streamlined and enjoyable experience, and working with them to achieve their personal and financial goals through real estate.<\/p><p>Brooks enjoys spending as much time as he can with his amazing family that has been supportive and his rock throughout his life. His wife Brittany, his son Graham, and his dog Harvey are his pride and joy. They love spending time outdoors, finding new restaurants, traveling, and spending time with extended family.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eae5fbf elementor-widget__width-auto e-transform elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eae5fbf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_transform_translateY_effect&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:12,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateX_effect&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateX_effect_widescreen&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateX_effect_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateX_effect_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateY_effect_widescreen&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateY_effect_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;_transform_translateY_effect_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&q